2026-01-12 13:38:34.283854+00	2026-01-12 13:38:34.283867+00	d5a52add-f70c-42f6-ab2c-86daf849e00f	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<ul><li><strong>\\"Equipment setup is standardized\\"</strong> - Various configurations exist based on diving goals and physical needs</li><li><strong>\\"Kids can't use digital learning\\"</strong> - Age-appropriate pathways exist with proper supervision</li><li><strong>\\"Instructors must teach in a fixed order\\"</strong> - Limited flexibility exists to arrange skills based on student comfort</li><li><strong>\\"The only path is Open Water  Advanced  Rescue  Divemaster\\"</strong> - Dozens of specialty courses offer different directions</li><li><strong>\\"Becoming an instructor requires being young\\"</strong> - Many become instructors later in life; judgment matters as much as water skills</li></ul>"}	19	t	6d8ca2d4-efc2-493c-8625-edac8f0ccb4a
