2026-01-12 15:31:00.488902+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.48891+00	16ea2de5-d85b-4899-ba2a-f814f3072255	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>This is basically what happened with me during the pandemic.</p>"}	0	t	b7d21f47-f572-4a37-a63f-8a1046952031
2026-01-12 15:31:00.497204+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.497212+00	37784a6a-56cc-44ff-b622-213d3355b0c0	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I began to collect it and untangle it from the corals it jerked and pulled very hard.  But whatever was hooked on the other end was stuck.</p><p>As I explored I saw this large ray caught.  It broke my heart to see it that way.  I was able to get close enought behind a coral to cut the line leaving about 5' dangliing from its mouth.  I hope it doesn't get caught up again.  Here it is after I rescued it.  It was very stressed, and I'm sure super tired and worn out from being stuck like that.  It immediately buried itself to hide and rest is what it looks like.</p>"}	0	t	5fd75608-477f-4c47-b22b-ec2665a5b9c0
2026-01-12 15:31:00.505577+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.505585+00	b25f8843-4ac8-4aac-9f90-3219dd3e95ed	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Ruth and Beto.  Borrowed his GoPro to more safely capture this magical lionfish moment for them.</p>"}	0	t	bea31f16-ce26-47c5-bb74-61fb501ba746
2026-01-12 15:31:00.513874+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.513882+00	4f3b9c58-44ee-4929-ab0d-dd34aa7df11c	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I really do love diving here alone by myself just the ocean, the creatures, and not too many thoughts.</p>"}	0	t	8f12a6e8-c936-42f1-9b0c-ae77901cfe5f
2026-01-12 15:31:00.521888+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.521896+00	badc6a3e-eab0-463a-a97a-3ea313f2b194	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Good day to relax and take myself diving again.</p><p>Yesterday made a full day of shore diving.  Guided 3 dive groups with a nice mix of 4 students and certified divers. Sucked the air out of 16 tanks. Most I've managed in a day so far new personal record.  Poco a poco. #happydiving #buceofeliz #puertomorelos #parquenacionalarrecifedepuertomorelos</p>"}	0	t	f84c6269-58d5-46b2-b9a6-e9ee2b0b7f8c
2026-01-12 15:31:00.531313+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.531325+00	c5d5ac75-66e5-49ea-9393-611fb954da6a	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Even after hundreds of times I'm still not bored.</p>"}	0	t	471632d9-9d4b-4129-bb3c-ba4b5ba1252d
2026-01-12 15:31:00.5481+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.54813+00	a761cc03-5938-46d7-a9fa-1cce5ca1d7fb	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Where it leaks is where I'll put the pee portal.</p>"}	0	t	58285903-e5d1-41cc-ad8a-675b4343499c
2026-01-12 15:31:00.561201+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.561213+00	209b8ac6-6275-49a3-8026-6c1b7af0fff7	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Total shit for visibility and an odd north current that moved up a bunch of crap in the water.   It's spooky and hard to navigate when things are turned around but it doesn't surprise me much anymore.  I do like how photos can turn out the colors are nice when the light is diffused like it is on the particulates.</p><p>The spotted moray eel I found is pretty.</p>"}	0	t	1f44143f-d1e5-49a9-b5d6-4ad6131c78cf
2026-01-12 15:31:00.571555+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.571565+00	912cf213-040a-4f24-8388-91139fc8baef	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>After nearly 300 dives it's time to change the battery.</p>"}	0	t	170e9c84-7161-4630-8022-2e7e8d5b99b4
2026-01-12 15:31:00.583894+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.58391+00	172998f3-cb7d-4032-bbda-3ac78d8db01d	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Weightbelt, some  fat O ring loops and a D ring to hold my buoy and camera, and a bungie cord.  Pretty comfortable.  Starts off a little heavy but nothing I can't swim up. We will see how it is to stay down when the tanks start getting empty.</p>"}	0	t	e7844de7-d118-4cd5-bbcb-ffdd568e94e1
2026-01-12 15:31:00.598802+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.598816+00	4f62a09a-a650-43ce-b0d8-75c1ac359fd5	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I took Nayeli on a dive today.  Boy there were a lot of fish, and the corals are still regaining symbionts.  The rain and the current we've had has been pushing out all the sargassum.  The visibility was not super great but when there are particles in the water it does make the colors really nice, especially the blue of the Carribbean.</p>"}	0	t	c1f309d1-ba46-441c-86fe-d78d13de275a
2026-01-12 15:31:00.610628+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.610639+00	31fc6e96-df75-4610-a163-ed20328808a6	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Apparently this is a thing and it's called \\\\</p>"}	0	t	6f18e3c8-a753-4f6b-bd78-7668d30560b5
2026-01-12 15:31:00.9393+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.939307+00	9b049284-a375-4b97-ae4d-3e3b86712a58	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Red flag day.  Choppy on top smooth and clear underneath.  My friend Tom's in town from Denver.  Wind's gonna die down and I'll bet when we go diving it's gonna be real nice.</p>"}	0	t	9f280826-3653-4b75-9750-e61f80339cfc
2026-01-12 15:31:00.620297+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.620306+00	ecf89800-5c83-47a2-8b58-4f426d04d7a0	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>We spent a lot of time just getting used to the feeling of our body in fluid space.  The feeling of breathing in an unnatural and otherwise deadly environment assisted by our life support SCUBA system.</p><p>Learning to control the mind and just breath and relax, practicing buoyancy on every single dive.  Especially early on in the training dives.  I think students benefit from more time practicing buoyancy and getting comfortable before introducing a lot of skills.</p><p>I emphasize swimming skills AKA \\\\</p>"}	0	t	bb6571dd-d1ed-49cf-98e2-c9748c6af578
2026-01-12 15:31:00.628941+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.628949+00	cc07f5bd-3a95-40a2-9943-5df6c8a0671a	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>There are many uses for cheap reusable food saver containers.  I've found a perfect fit for my wide angle lens</p>"}	0	t	20e2e6b6-44d4-4c1d-97dd-3ec34f12fbb7
2026-01-12 15:31:00.637057+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.637065+00	874b41de-f69c-41a0-8575-8687ec603216	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Mock up of my branding watermark.   I will have some time during this upcoming trip to nerd out and write a program to automate this process.</p>"}	0	t	eaec8279-8121-4644-888c-6ae7bec28d2f
2026-01-12 15:31:00.645479+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.645487+00	9df4c148-7b77-49cb-9cce-59df3e2a1283	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Maybe I'll get some dives in back home in Missouri during my visit.  But I fly out in two days and I've been diving a lot so I'm going to take a dip this morning and then that will be it before I fly back to the states.</p><p>This cylinder has enough gas for about 50 min of shore diving.</p>"}	0	t	dfed92b9-1e9c-4023-8877-56fe2d539d95
2026-01-12 15:31:00.653761+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.653771+00	2a8e022d-0574-4058-a801-ec485b0a62c1	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>It all starts with good scuba swimming and buoyancy skills.  It's contrary at first to how you're used to swimming.  Because we don't use our arms/hands for propulsion.  Rather we use our fins and keep our hands free for other tasks, like using a compass when the visibility is bad and we need to find our way without getting lost.</p>"}	0	t	3f2b1e64-d499-48dd-9007-41c96c796edd
2026-01-12 15:31:00.661911+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.661919+00	6f8a1531-4f0e-4156-bd94-ea1b4260e716	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Geoff, Beto, and I went diving today.  Beto worked on his underwater photography while I taught Geoff some important scuba skills as part of his open water course/</p><p>More pictures of our adventures will be forthcoming.  Butt tonight we're all pretty whipped.  It's been a lot of diving.</p>"}	0	t	326d5a77-e2c3-4ac0-ab8a-11268b94b0f4
2026-01-12 15:31:00.669965+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.669973+00	260f7b8e-35e2-4b2b-b92e-04efaf310ec8	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Post diving two for one at Blu with Geoff and Mette.</p><p>I really enjoy being able to guide my out of town friends on the reef, and to favorite places my local friends and I frequent.</p>"}	0	t	69f691a5-2216-4947-9367-a50534f61515
2026-01-12 15:31:00.678521+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.678529+00	fb42be89-44cb-4ad3-bf52-6531d5552c86	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Today I got back from some errands in Cancun and had enough time for a dive.  So I hitched a ride with my buuddy David and Victor and they dropped me at the shore where I dove a little under 1/2 a tank in the Lagoon for 56 minutes.  Then I walked about a block and met them for a beer and hitched a ride back.  That leaves me another long shallow dive on the same tank, woot!</p>"}	0	t	e097d5c6-86d9-4d3c-9847-94039a14d047
2026-01-12 15:31:00.686774+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.686782+00	6fbe1f17-634a-491e-af93-01aa5d6f0d85	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Super excited for Geoffrey and Mette here for a visit from St Louis.  We got the guest room ready here at our little sometimes Mexican Bed and Breakfast house.  Alberto cooked huevos Mexicana for today's breakfast.</p><p>Geoffrey is coming to do diving and Mette came for the beach.  I took her to the port yesterday after her flight arrived and she had an easy trouble free flight into and pre arranged ride from Cancun.</p><p>In Puerto Morelos it was a beautiful night to watch the sunset from the pier.</p><p>Visiting #puertomorelos my OG friends from  #gatewayburners are here for some #happydiving with #padipro yours truly.</p>"}	0	t	1dd049f2-97a4-4de4-854c-82ed6896cc06
2026-01-12 15:31:00.695205+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.695213+00	a21e4840-e4ee-4992-a446-b5b917d99768	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Part of the thrill of deeper diving is looking up and seeing the way the light diffuses when there are a lot of particles in the current.  The line eventually ends at the surface.  That surface is still pretty far away beyond what you can see here.</p>"}	0	t	5ffd9349-2a5d-42e6-b032-9eeae1234787
2026-01-12 15:31:00.70347+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.703478+00	a0e1d925-2a05-4cf0-bf62-a8ad954ae88e	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I'm revisiting some photos I took almost 2 years ago when I first started diving here in Puerto Morelos.  While my diving was still undergoing rapid transformation, the photogoraphy skills I'd been practicing decades by that point made up for my beginner buoyancy.</p><p>Fast forward a bit and I'm applying some post production tricks I've learned for underwater photography since.  I love this dive site, I'm trying to remember the name I think Jardines is what my underwater photographer friend here tells me maybe it is.</p><p>Estoy revisando algunas fotos que tom\\\\u00e9 hace casi 2 a\\\\u00f1os cuando comenc\\\\u00e9 a bucear aqu\\\\u00ed en Puerto Morelos. Si bien mi buceo todav\\\\u00eda estaba experimentando una r\\\\u00e1pida transformaci\\\\u00f3n, las habilidades de fotograf\\\\u00eda que hab\\\\u00eda estado practicando durante d\\\\u00e9cadas en ese momento compensaron mi flotabilidad de principiante.</p><p>Avance un poco y estoy aplicando algunos trucos de postproducci\\\\u00f3n que he aprendido para la fotograf\\\\u00eda submarina desde entonces. Me encanta este sitio de buceo, estoy tratando de recordar el nombre, creo que Jardines es lo que mi amigo fot\\\\u00f3grafo submarino aqu\\\\u00ed me dice que tal vez sea.</p>"}	0	t	6184affc-c542-436b-b083-c6dcaa23c736
2026-01-12 15:31:00.711824+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.711832+00	8d5399c7-80ad-4437-8145-c260b6f35649	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>OMG there is a Border Collie Group here</p>"}	0	t	81fc5698-b634-4079-8614-42a4f9ec6e29
2026-01-12 15:31:00.720025+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.720033+00	539e3061-fb08-457b-9141-2571e5575aa9	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Lol because you never know when you'll need a snorkel in a cave.</p>"}	0	t	df9b98dd-9487-49a7-a08c-bbbd89792a96
2026-01-12 15:31:00.728327+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.728334+00	bbc7f071-50c2-486d-bbc2-3b90381ee547	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>A remora is fascinated with Beto's leg area.</p>"}	0	t	6e73e699-77ea-420a-96ec-aa2123dd5b75
2026-01-12 15:31:00.736818+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.736826+00	c1498171-4536-4c1e-8954-8ddcaef05312	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>noun: skin-diver; plural noun: skin-divers\\na person who engages in the sport or activity of skin diving.\\n\\\\</p>"}	0	t	88c800bb-1c0a-414b-9d35-72d5837ab639
2026-01-12 15:31:00.74481+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.744818+00	fdf07118-8850-4615-8552-80719dd7d79d	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>The diving yesterday was pretty fantastic.</p>"}	0	t	b8769550-2cdf-425e-8291-4b1adc45c760
2026-01-12 15:31:00.752873+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.752881+00	629b758d-0a5d-49cf-9777-66570ed7cf98	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Join the team!\\nWe have 2 instructor/dive guide/mate positions available. We teach SDI and PADI.\\nPlease call or email your CV if you would like to join the JDC family.</p><p>561-745-7807\\nLisa\\\\u0040jupiterdivecenter.com</p>"}	0	t	3f3aa078-4261-418f-acff-5bb769962ffd
2026-01-12 15:31:00.761201+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.761209+00	e51114b2-aa36-406c-bd33-ba371c7570b9	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>If you practice pacing your CESA exhalation before you get into the water you're going to have no problems succeeding.   Check out my video on my new YouTube channel.  Please like and subscribe.  \\nhttps://youtu.be/zwXFObh0x0w</p>"}	0	t	e7ad5432-650e-47b1-859c-3c7504ca41af
2026-01-12 15:31:00.769568+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.769576+00	83c88ccd-d4fd-4ba2-83f4-edbf91d11434	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Sounds like a dangerous fool's errand. Just because you can dive doesn't mean you should ever take up an offer to find someone's wife's phone they dropped in a boat channel.  #badidea jeans</p>"}	0	t	ef0ec649-f973-4af4-afdf-fbd138cbb71f
2026-01-12 15:31:00.777807+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.777815+00	103e0c0e-d57d-40dc-98c7-1d42eab7500a	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>During the day the puffers are wary and easily frightened away.  At night however, it's like they're so asleep they don't even notice the bubbles, lights, or the flash from the camera.</p>"}	0	t	dfd5d02d-0e3e-414c-954c-556aa0862a58
2026-01-12 15:31:00.78602+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.786029+00	5e79da12-fa45-4663-99a9-0f717e4e4957	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I picked up this awesome notebook at a local paper store to keep diving related notes ideas sketches, commonplaces, and other things.</p><p>Sometimes I find hand writing is oftentimes a good way to stimulate , rehearse, and organize thoughts.  Here I made a list of words that come to mind about diving.</p><p>If you think of a word not on the list please add it below.  Or just a few of your own favorite words as they come time mind is fine too.</p>"}	0	t	3030ef44-b4cd-441c-be0e-590af0451ae3
2026-01-12 15:31:00.794565+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.794573+00	5a8ddb51-1f3b-4b63-82d0-06d45ba619bc	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>The local moray.  I'm starting to wonder if there are different ones that come in and out since I've seen two during one dive before.  And this one looks different it has what appears to be some scarring and bite marks(?) under its jaw there.</p><p>I've started losing my super creeped out feeling around them (they have an alien jaw!!).  I calmly hung out near it (about 2m) and It didn't pay me any attention for a good 15 minutes while I blew some bubbles and took photos.</p>"}	0	t	900ccf21-46e3-4d1d-a332-a62e1938d4fe
2026-01-12 15:31:00.802858+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.802872+00	5a4f5a28-fc99-4632-9589-a096cd88406e	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I have an idea to try on a dive today to reduce backscatter while still triggering the manual external strobe.</p>"}	0	t	02a201bb-56eb-4a48-8653-b145953d59d9
2026-01-12 15:31:00.812847+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.812855+00	8a3fd96a-1dcc-43c2-bcd4-e151aa21a452	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I don't think you could ask for a nicer day to swim in the ocean and blow bubbles.</p>"}	0	t	c1e9572c-9161-4674-bc17-aac518e360a0
2026-01-12 15:31:00.821332+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.82134+00	fe1ca822-6bc0-4156-8a5e-efc2fc91cc92	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>This is so cool and very unexpected.  I try pretty hard to stimulate participation and enjoyment of the undersea world though my photography.  I think it's a new facebook record for folks enjoying and commenting on my work.  Such a nice fuzzy feeling that quite a few people actually like what I'm doing.  Thanks everyone reading this!</p>"}	0	t	9a92364c-1f96-4998-aa6e-bcfaaa603465
2026-01-12 15:31:00.829544+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.829552+00	b0b9f8b5-24e4-44d1-9f33-9c770a977a9f	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Sargassum stipe, blade, and bladder.</p>"}	0	t	ae1ac4e3-a9d0-49eb-a83e-4e2218fd7a78
2026-01-12 15:31:00.837002+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.83701+00	73ea8861-5c57-41c8-8577-09916875c1c4	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Ocean Triggerfish.  I read they hang out at 35'-100' but I see them frequently in 10' of water.  Maybe they are just passing through because I've never run into an aggressive territorial one (yet).</p>"}	0	t	6467f60d-bf1a-4c90-b1a0-13bb0e34110c
2026-01-12 15:31:00.845079+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.845086+00	b15efc02-da1e-4ed7-8409-e90faca77f91	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>An old concrete mooring  has turned into a reef habitat shared by many creatures.</p>"}	0	t	b2fbad27-250e-4969-a75e-3aa7012ca42c
2026-01-12 15:31:00.852113+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.852126+00	32dd5986-7074-4bc7-a653-02237040bf01	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>A lot of divers know it's best to avoid fire coral to save themselves from a nasty sting and a lingering rash.  But you might not know about these hydrozoans pictured here that are seemingly innocuous little tufts of what could easily be mistaken for some sargassum.  But they pack a punch when they sting you.  If you look close you can see the hairlike appendages that are waiting to detect a stimulus and fire a projectile barb with a toxin into your skin.  Just like a jellyfish.  So don't touch them.</p>"}	0	t	62b23d1e-0356-421f-85e7-186903122ed2
2026-01-12 15:31:00.859957+00	2026-01-12 15:31:00.859964+00	09103c1e-b322-4f25-bb1f-ffe9e1263a03	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I always love visiting the puffers.  It's so calm just to chill out and float next to them.  You looking at them.  Them looking at you.</p>"}	0	t	c3735d61-14e1-4b61-9540-d16ff37f1439
