2026-01-12 15:31:01.338075+00	2026-01-12 15:31:01.338085+00	8aab2999-4117-4741-8343-28b5068dc8b8	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>I\\\\u2019m officially an advanced adaptive dive buddy! Regardless of what differences you might have you can likely learn to dive. I am so in awe of this week and I also believe we can always do better.</p>"}	0	t	d9b47a85-55f5-4f9d-9e2c-08135146835d
2026-01-12 15:31:01.352685+00	2026-01-12 15:31:01.352691+00	88540df6-bfc9-4de6-a12b-7f6477608275	\N	rich_text	{"content": "<p>Herald and I have been diving a lot this week.  He's been learning the PADI open water course with me.  This dude is a natural.  It's been great teaching one on one in the ocean.</p>"}	0	t	7ab67066-4c54-4f39-9b59-0211b32df75b
