2026-01-12 15:31:00.495056+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.657995+00	5fd75608-477f-4c47-b22b-ec2665a5b9c0	\N	2024-01-15-today-i-went-diving-and-saw	Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I b...	published	public	[]	[]	Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I b...	Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I began to collect it and untangle it from the corals it jerked and pulled very hard....			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2024-01-15-today-i-went-diving-and-saw/", "slug": "2024-01-15-today-i-went-diving-and-saw", "title": "Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I b...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I b...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I began to collect it and untangle it from the corals it jerked and pulled very hard...."}, "blocks": [{"id": "37784a6a-56cc-44ff-b622-213d3355b0c0", "data": {"content": "<p>Today I went diving and saw a great deal of fishing line and as I began to collect it and untangle it from the corals it jerked and pulled very hard.  But whatever was hooked on the other end was stuck.</p><p>As I explored I saw this large ray caught.  It broke my heart to see it that way.  I was able to get close enought behind a coral to cut the line leaving about 5' dangliing from its mouth.  I hope it doesn't get caught up again.  Here it is after I rescued it.  It was very stressed, and I'm sure super tired and worn out from being stuck like that.  It immediately buried itself to hide and rest is what it looks like.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "fec58646bcf77ad698bd23ace7437793f047600c4092b7d5210d62364affdecb", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:00.500390+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-0