2026-01-12 15:31:01.249899+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.505313+00	23d22df7-1e20-43d9-9822-46682534244f	\N	2022-12-27-the-rain-pours-down-in-sheets	The rain pours down in sheets of gray,	published	public	[]	[]	The rain pours down in sheets of gray,	The rain pours down in sheets of gray, The harbor closed, a red flag on display. The winds howl, the waves crash and roar, Scuba diving plans, we can...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-12-27-the-rain-pours-down-in-sheets/", "slug": "2022-12-27-the-rain-pours-down-in-sheets", "title": "The rain pours down in sheets of gray,", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "The rain pours down in sheets of gray,", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "The rain pours down in sheets of gray, The harbor closed, a red flag on display. The winds howl, the waves crash and roar, Scuba diving plans, we can..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "39c0a0fe-dac3-4767-ac51-79b52136a946", "data": {"content": "<p>The rain pours down in sheets of gray,\\nThe harbor closed, a red flag on display.</p><p>The winds howl, the waves crash and roar,\\nScuba diving plans, we can do no more.</p><p>We watch from shore as the storm rages on,\\nLonging to dive, but the weather is too strong.</p><p>We wait for the calm, for the sun to shine,\\nFor the red flag to be taken down, to be free to dive.</p><p>But until then, we sit and we dream,\\nOf the underwater world, so clear and serene.</p><p>So let the rain fall, let the winds blow,\\nWe'll bide our time, and scuba dive when we go.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "66cd1ffd0244ed5455bf5259365c5b3e09899e86d1ca3b47374aa95fa9ed994c", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.254489+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.254489+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-12-27"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	The rain pours down in sheets of gray, The harbor close