fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/470208187_905915178192121_1823335825300938662_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s590x590_tt6&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=127cfc&_nc_ohc=0-fXZCw2p5IQ7kNvwHxH-JA&_nc_oc=Adl14jwLWexW0XtnF3V_GkjSTJ2JD0LPgUBXOykGNTO2PM42zC6b-YtVUtw1itp0ae8&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=m4HwkCu9EJZhLF-kqhaf6w&oh=00_AfpmZHx_yEqGdtFjTkTEw_vJ4pHdnylLrGLyhLgXNT7E6w&oe=696AC286	post	1	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	4b2ed9e6-5050-4544-ac4a-cf4f2c8ac7bb
2026-01-12 15:31:01.233426+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.509462+00	123f238e-4561-48e6-be0f-dcf5c40a538f	\N	2022-12-31-im-keeping-busy-on-these-no	I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online lear...	published	public	[]	[]	I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online lear...	I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online learning and diver management system. The abstract goals I have in mind are to...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-12-31-im-keeping-busy-on-these-no/", "slug": "2022-12-31-im-keeping-busy-on-these-no", "title": "I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online lear...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online lear...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online learning and diver management system. The abstract goals I have in mind are to..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "bd37c8b0-37d4-4343-990e-ec7ed7720120", "data": {"content": "<p>I'm keeping busy on these no diving days by planning my online learning and diver management system. The abstract goals I have in mind are to efficiently centralize and interact with information stored in a SQL database using an ERP system and automate as many clerical tasks as possible.</p><p>Many of you may know that I have two decades of experience now developing applications on Linux servers with open source software.  Today I will be installing Ubuntu Server on a small Alienware gaming machine I brought to Mexico.  I hope to utilize it's graphics card for some Artificial Intelligence tasks to help me with photography post-production and automated image classification.</p><p>So how in the world you may wonder does someone have a similar attraction to diving and computer technology?!! And how does that interest light up a lot of the same areas of my brain?  And maybe yours too? Feel free to sound in if you think you're also interested in diving and technology.  I'm looking for out of the water coding buddies to play with.</p><p>Scuba diving and software development both involve working with complex systems and problem-solving to ensure the safe and efficient functioning of those systems. In scuba diving, this includes maintaining and repairing diving equipment, planning and executing dive plans, and responding to issues that may arise during a dive. Similarly, in software development, this involves designing and building software systems, debugging and troubleshooting issues, and maintaining and updating existing systems.</p><p>Both scuba diving and software development also require a strong attention to detail and the ability to think critically and logically. In scuba diving, small mistakes or oversights can have serious consequences, so it is important to be diligent in checking and double-checking equipment and following safety procedures. In software development, it is important to accurately and thoroughly test and debug code to ensure that the software functions as intended and does not contain any errors or vulnerabilities.</p><p>Both scuba diving and software development can also be rewarding and enjoyable for people who enjoy learning new things and tackling challenging problems. In scuba diving, there is always something new to discover and explore, whether it is a new dive site or a new type of marine life. Similarly, in software development, there is always the opportunity to learn new technologies and techniques, and to tackle complex and interesting problems.</p><p>One of the first interesting problems I may tackle is writing a tank tracker and EANx Nitrox fill log system that I can provide to my students and other divers to suppliment the Nitrox course I teach.  Now that I own 17 tanks It's important to keep information about the entire lifecycle such as maintenance and fill records, their current locations, and if they are available to rent to other divers.</p><p>---</p><p>Me mantengo ocupado en estos d\\\\u00edas sin bucear planificando mi aprendizaje en l\\\\u00ednea y el sistema de gesti\\\\u00f3n de buceadores. Los objetivos abstractos que tengo en mente son centralizar e interactuar de manera eficiente con la informaci\\\\u00f3n almacenada en una base de datos SQL utilizando un sistema ERP y automatizar tantas tareas administrativas como sea posible.</p><p>Muchos de ustedes pueden saber que tengo dos d\\\\u00e9cadas de experiencia en el desarrollo de aplicaciones en servidores Linux con software de c\\\\u00f3digo abierto. Hoy instalar\\\\u00e9 Ubuntu Server en una peque\\\\u00f1a m\\\\u00e1quina de juegos Alienware que traje a M\\\\u00e9xico. Espero utilizar su tarjeta gr\\\\u00e1fica para algunas tareas de inteligencia artificial que me ayuden con la posproducci\\\\u00f3n de fotograf\\\\u00edas y la clasificaci\\\\u00f3n automatizada de im\\\\u00e1genes.</p><p>Entonces, \\\\u00bfc\\\\u00f3mo es posible que te preguntes si alguien tiene una atracci\\\\u00f3n similar por el buceo y la tecnolog\\\\u00eda inform\\\\u00e1tica? \\\\u00bfY c\\\\u00f3mo ese inter\\\\u00e9s ilumina muchas de las mismas \\\\u00e1reas de mi cerebro? \\\\u00bfY quiz\\\\u00e1s el tuyo tambi\\\\u00e9n? Si\\\\u00e9ntase libre de participar si cree que tambi\\\\u00e9n est\\\\u00e1 interesado en el buceo y la tecnolog\\\\u00eda. Estoy buscando amigos de codificaci\\\\u00f3n fuera del agua para jugar.</p><p>El buceo y el desarrollo de software implican trabajar con sistemas complejos y resolver problemas para garantizar el funcionamiento seguro y eficiente de esos sistemas. En el buceo, esto incluye mantener y reparar el equipo de buceo, planificar y ejecutar planes de buceo y responder a los problemas que puedan surgir durante una inmersi\\\\u00f3n. De manera similar, en el desarrollo de software, esto implica dise\\\\u00f1ar y construir sistemas de software, depurar y solucionar problemas, y mantener y actualizar los sistemas existentes.</p><p>Tanto el buceo como el desarrollo de software tambi\\\\u00e9n requieren una gran atenci\\\\u00f3n a los detalles y la capacidad de pensar de forma cr\\\\u00edtica y l\\\\u00f3gica. En el buceo, los peque\\\\u00f1os errores o descuidos pueden tener graves consecuencias, por lo que es importante ser diligentes en la verificaci\\\\u00f3n y doble verificaci\\\\u00f3n del equipo y seguir los procedimientos de seguridad. En el desarrollo de software, es importante probar y depurar el c\\\\u00f3digo de manera precisa y exhaustiva para garantizar que el software funcione seg\\\\u00fan lo previsto y no contenga errores ni vulnerabilidades.</p><p>Tanto el buceo como el desarrollo de software tambi\\\\u00e9n pueden ser gratificantes y agradables para las personas que disfrutan aprendiendo cosas nuevas y abordando problemas desafiantes. En el buceo, siempre hay algo nuevo que descubrir y explorar, ya sea un nuevo sitio de buceo o un nuevo tipo de vida marina. De manera similar, en el desarrollo de software, siempre existe la oportunidad de aprender nuevas tecnolog\\\\u00edas y t\\\\u00e9cnicas, y de abordar problemas complejos e interesantes.</p><p>Uno de los primeros problemas interesantes que puedo abordar es escribir un rastreador de tanques y un sistema de registro de llenado de Nitrox EANx que pueda proporcionar a mis alumnos y otros buceadores para complementar el curso de Nitrox que ense\\\\u00f1o.</p><p>Ahora que tengo 17 tanques, es importante mantener informaci\\\\u00f3n sobre todo el ciclo de vida, como registros de mantenimiento y llenado, sus ubicaciones actuales y si est\\\\u00e1n disponibles para alquilar a otros buceadores.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "91264986a880a99b9c274d43d9c45b74d89414d0bff803afeb657cfdcf59e79e", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.238635+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.238635+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "