2026-01-12 15:31:01.412035+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.457398+00	a23c95f4-22f4-434c-949a-dfc0976f7c20	\N	2022-10-15-went-diving-yesterday-with-a-couple	Went diving yesterday with a couple friends.  We saw a ton of stuff...	published	public	[]	[]	Went diving yesterday with a couple friends.  We saw a ton of stuff...	Went diving yesterday with a couple friends. We saw a ton of stuff. On the way down we were startled with a surprise stingray camouflaged in the grass...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-10-15-went-diving-yesterday-with-a-couple/", "slug": "2022-10-15-went-diving-yesterday-with-a-couple", "title": "Went diving yesterday with a couple friends.  We saw a ton of stuff...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Went diving yesterday with a couple friends.  We saw a ton of stuff...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Went diving yesterday with a couple friends. We saw a ton of stuff. On the way down we were startled with a surprise stingray camouflaged in the grass..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "6031c973-0f1c-4ce0-9eae-2ddbf84ba03c", "data": {"content": "<p>Went diving yesterday with a couple friends.  We saw a ton of stuff. On the way down we were startled with a surprise stingray camouflaged in the grass that appeared suddenly out of the silt.  But when I was taking it's photo it didn't care it let me get super close and didn't care one bit when I sailed over it.</p><p>We navigated to many of the coral formations and other interesting features of the dive site.  Despite the poorer visibility that day we were able to find some pretty large schools of fish.  We were able to swim with the resident school of Atlantic Spade fish which was super fun, they were all over us.</p><p>I hadn't seen the large Moray Eel in a while.  But there it was near the end of the dive tucked under one of the corals.  Unfortunately the lighting wasn't super great and I felt kind of apprehensive about getting in super close with the camera in its face for a good shot.  Maybe in the future I'll get more courage or else I'll learn better lighting and when the visibility is much better.</p><p>---</p><p>Fui a bucear ayer con un par de amigos. Vimos un mont\\\\u00f3n de cosas. En el camino hacia abajo nos sorprendi\\\\u00f3 una mantarraya camuflada en la hierba que apareci\\\\u00f3 repentinamente del limo. Pero cuando estaba tomando la foto, no le import\\\\u00f3, me dej\\\\u00f3 acercarme mucho y no le import\\\\u00f3 ni un poco cuando navegu\\\\u00e9 sobre ella.</p><p>Navegamos a muchas de las formaciones de coral y otras caracter\\\\u00edsticas interesantes del sitio de buceo. A pesar de la poca visibilidad ese d\\\\u00eda, pudimos encontrar algunos bancos de peces bastante grandes. Pudimos nadar con la escuela residente de peces Atlantic Spade, que fue muy divertido, estaban sobre nosotros.</p><p>No hab\\\\u00eda visto la gran Moray Eel en mucho tiempo. Pero all\\\\u00ed estaba, cerca del final de la inmersi\\\\u00f3n, escondido debajo de uno de los corales. Desafortunadamente, la iluminaci\\\\u00f3n no era muy buena y me sent\\\\u00ed un poco aprensivo acerca de acercarme mucho a la c\\\\u00e1mara para obtener una buena toma. Tal vez en el futuro me anime m\\\\u00e1s o de lo contrario aprender\\\\u00e9 a iluminar mejor y cuando la visibilidad sea mucho mejor.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "f6038421c98846a2db367d9700e6b7d76d58780c10ec1ddeb5b7cecdf63d1eec", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.415562+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.415562+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-10-15"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	Went diving yesterday with a couple friends. We saw a ton of stuff. On the way down we were startled with a surprise stingray camouflaged in the grass that appeared suddenly out of the silt. But...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/48