2026-01-12 15:31:01.571011+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.414813+00	1d863c39-3f6d-422d-ac9f-e8f7cc51b5fd	\N	2022-09-16-i-had-a-nice-visit-with	I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close t...	published	public	[]	[]	I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close t...	I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close to my folks in Florida. They come to Mexico regularly and it was Terrena's birthday...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-09-16-i-had-a-nice-visit-with/", "slug": "2022-09-16-i-had-a-nice-visit-with", "title": "I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close t...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close t...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close to my folks in Florida. They come to Mexico regularly and it was Terrena's birthday..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "35cb1d45-72c7-4585-9d9f-2d1959f7a96a", "data": {"content": "<p>I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close to my folks in Florida.  They come to Mexico regularly and it was Terrena's birthday week vacation so they hit me up to have a nice afternoon on the beach followed by a lunch at La Caba\\\\u00f1a.  It was their first visit to the Colonia side and it was a real pleaser.  They both appreciated the authentic part of town where I live.</p><p>Jim and I went on a little shore dive for fun together and saw a lot of fish and and corals as I gave him a tour of one of my favorite dive sites.  Jim loved it and agreed it's the best shore dive he's ever done.</p><p>Where they are from in Florida on the Gulf side getting to a decent dive site is 50 miles out on a boat.  Or a drive across the peninsula to the east coast to dive in the Atlantic or down to the keys.  I'm looking forward on my next visit to my folks to hopefully take a trip to a Florida dive site and go diving again togethe soon.</p><p>Tuve una agradable visita con mis amigos Terrena y Jim que viven cerca de mis padres en Florida. Vienen a M\\\\u00e9xico con regularidad y era la semana de vacaciones del cumplea\\\\u00f1os de Terrena, as\\\\u00ed que me llamaron para pasar una agradable tarde en la playa seguida de un almuerzo en La Caba\\\\u00f1a. Era su primera visita al lado de Colonia y fue un verdadero placer. Ambos apreciaron la parte aut\\\\u00e9ntica de la ciudad donde vivo.</p><p>Jim y yo hicimos un peque\\\\u00f1o buceo en la costa para divertirnos juntos y vimos muchos peces y corales mientras le daba un recorrido por uno de mis sitios de buceo favoritos. A Jim le encant\\\\u00f3 y estuvo de acuerdo en que es la mejor inmersi\\\\u00f3n en tierra que ha hecho.</p><p>De donde son en Florida en el lado del Golfo, llegar a un sitio de buceo decente est\\\\u00e1 a 50 millas en un bote. O un paseo por la pen\\\\u00ednsula hasta la costa este para bucear en el Atl\\\\u00e1ntico o bajar a los cayos. Espero con ansias la pr\\\\u00f3xima visita a mis padres para hacer un viaje a un sitio de buceo de Florida y volver a bucear juntos pronto.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "617e0215a01be70230820d2cdd658fa6f5c26a226ae148964bca3744679c72e9", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.576933+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.576933+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-09-16"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	I had a nice visit with my friends Terrena and Jim who live close to my folks in Florida. They come to Mexico regularly and it was Terrena's birthday week vacation so they hit me up to have a nice...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/470145831_905923908191248_7940697876319809308_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s590x590_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=833d8c&_nc_ohc=sdUW4AwuprgQ7kNvwGcNJLO&_nc_oc=AdmxSXUD-byuNUI823