2026-01-12 15:31:01.471492+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.437144+00	35673bbf-651c-40c6-8d23-f91f50565f6b	\N	2022-10-03-whenever-i-take-someones-backwards-rollback	Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I...	published	public	[]	[]	Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I...	Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I like to capture it for our scubafans, jajaja.  Here is Bill's first time rolling...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-10-03-whenever-i-take-someones-backwards-rollback/", "slug": "2022-10-03-whenever-i-take-someones-backwards-rollback", "title": "Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I like to capture it for our scubafans, jajaja.  Here is Bill's first time rolling..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "1f0a7524-b547-441d-9707-5166aee6a538", "data": {"content": "<p>Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I like to capture it for our scubafans, jajaja.   Here is Bill's first time rolling backwards off a boat.  Great job Bill!  It takes a lot of courage the first time.  Thanks Alberto for demonstrating.</p><p>Pro Tip: Next time also hold your mask with your fingers while you hold your regulator.  Excellent job on protecting your head!</p><p>As always a huge thanks to our Capitan Larry and his awesome vessel Rubia for the charter.  Having a competent captain with 28 years of diving experience and a better than most seaworthy vessel with a good reliable and fast engine makes all the difference for a safe fun dive.</p><p>Captain Larry has been my mentor helping me and my friends to learn how ocean boat diving is done right!  I can't thank him enough for helping us to become better safer divers, following our bubbles, and never losing track of where we are.</p><p>Two of my biggest fears are being struck by a propeller on the surface or being lost by the boat.  Every time we surface we can count on the Rubia safely being there waiting for us with the propeller disengaged and Larry fully aware of every diver in the water like a momma duck counting her ducklings!</p><p>-----</p><p>Cada vez que tomo la virginidad de la entrada del barco al rev\\\\u00e9s de alguien, me gusta capturarla para nuestros fan\\\\u00e1ticos del buceo, jajaja. Esta es la primera vez que Bill rueda hacia atr\\\\u00e1s desde un bote. \\\\u00a1Buen trabajo Bill! Se necesita mucho coraje la primera vez. Gracias Alberto por demostrar.</p><p>Consejo profesional: la pr\\\\u00f3xima vez sostenga tambi\\\\u00e9n la m\\\\u00e1scara con los dedos mientras sostiene el regulador. \\\\u00a1Excelente trabajo protegiendo tu cabeza!</p><p>Como siempre, muchas gracias a nuestro Capit\\\\u00e1n Larry y su impresionante barco Rubia por el alquiler. Tener un capit\\\\u00e1n competente con 28 a\\\\u00f1os de experiencia en buceo y una embarcaci\\\\u00f3n mejor que la mayor\\\\u00eda en condiciones de navegar con un buen motor confiable y r\\\\u00e1pido marca la diferencia para una inmersi\\\\u00f3n segura y divertida.</p><p>\\\\u00a1El Capit\\\\u00e1n Larry ha sido mi mentor y nos ha ayudado a m\\\\u00ed y a mis amigos a aprender c\\\\u00f3mo se hace bien el buceo en barco en el oc\\\\u00e9ano! No puedo agradecerle lo suficiente por ayudarnos a convertirnos en buceadores m\\\\u00e1s seguros, siguiendo nuestras burbujas y sin perder nunca la noci\\\\u00f3n de d\\\\u00f3nde estamos.</p><p>Dos de mis mayores temores son que me golpee una h\\\\u00e9lice en la superficie o que me pierda el barco. \\\\u00a1Cada vez que salimos a la superficie, podemos contar con que la Rubia estar\\\\u00e1 all\\\\u00ed esper\\\\u00e1ndonos con la h\\\\u00e9lice desconectada y Larry completamente consciente de cada buzo en el agua como una mam\\\\u00e1 pato contando sus patitos!</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "d4b8b91682c9a1bba6c8aeef12bcf2c1de62bd11f6fe1ca8945774be6f19c84b", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.475752+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.475752+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-10-03"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	Whenever I take someone's backwards rollback boat entry virginity I like to capture it for our scubafans, jajaja.  Here is Bill's first time rolling backwards off a boat. Great job Bill! It takes...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/487662611_1045817230898473_2231454743536626509_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s590x590_tt6&_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=833d8c&_nc_ohc=7jQsk_dsp74Q7kNvwErAlEm&_nc_oc=AdkwsEuqtpzxzdDc4-N0OxSWk-fE2ZkLYzwnyLkf8dmQzwnbfmbiJxdlwNx42Iofzm0&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=tyBhz9uJBk7spLBS8VCBxA&oh=00_AfpdtV3xvTdMaQ2IsXBddA94ikjLVXHF8l1tRScXKdfnyg&oe=696ADD2D	post	2	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	4b2ed9e6-5050-4544-ac4a-cf4f2c8ac7bb
