2026-01-12 15:31:01.626783+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.402053+00	5c7e0e4c-a783-4404-b9bb-dcd2c0280079	\N	2022-09-08-sidemount-practice-today-let-me-just	Sidemount practice today.  Let me just say I love this way of divin...	published	public	[]	[]	Sidemount practice today.  Let me just say I love this way of divin...	Sidemount practice today. Let me just say I love this way of diving. The buoyancy and trim was not too hard to learn and once I did it's much easier on...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-09-08-sidemount-practice-today-let-me-just/", "slug": "2022-09-08-sidemount-practice-today-let-me-just", "title": "Sidemount practice today.  Let me just say I love this way of divin...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Sidemount practice today.  Let me just say I love this way of divin...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Sidemount practice today. Let me just say I love this way of diving. The buoyancy and trim was not too hard to learn and once I did it's much easier on..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "a791b290-6bd8-45c5-9378-96bae7b8628f", "data": {"content": "<p>Sidemount practice today.  Let me just say I love this way of diving.  The buoyancy and trim was not too hard to learn and once I did it's much easier on my back then back mount.  The maneuverability is much better.  And as far as effort needed for moving the tanks and the gear from the taxi to the beach goes it's almost on par with diving a backplate and wing with weights and all the things in terms of weight and is I'd say it's just as much weight to carry when I bring a pony.  Also my shoulders feel a lot better from not carrying a tank on my back.  A bonus of course is the redundancy and self-reliant safety that you get and of course the time underwater is doubled on this particular shore dive when deco isn't really a concern.  Full cave cert course starts 9/20.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "54aeb564d469406acd63b3d9287282d9f0ee0f379173e1315146480aa3b2