2026-01-12 15:31:01.595771+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.409159+00	ea986399-0821-4f25-931d-95198ed5584c	\N	2022-09-12-took-alberto-on-a-dive-and	Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for ...	published	public	[]	[]	Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for ...	Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for his PADI Advanced Open Water Diver course. The way I'm teaching him navigation is...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-09-12-took-alberto-on-a-dive-and/", "slug": "2022-09-12-took-alberto-on-a-dive-and", "title": "Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for ...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for ...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for his PADI Advanced Open Water Diver course. The way I'm teaching him navigation is..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "cf50a243-f5b5-4f12-a44b-2462b4a5aed2", "data": {"content": "<p>Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for his PADI Advanced Open Water Diver course.</p><p>The way I'm teaching him navigation is hands on.  He's a cartographer so we're making it more interesting and broader by mapping the features and attractions of Ojo De Agua, the shore diving area in Puerto Morelos Mexico.</p><p>Our plan is for both of us to have fun while improving our underwater navigation skills while we create a scuba trail that can be used for the Navigation course for future students and others who have an interest in having a map to discover the lagoon.</p><p>We will include additional map layers from data sources from the National Park and also interactive images and videos with geotagging so people can see what fun they can have diving here.  #happydiving #buceofeliz #padiinstructor</p><p>----</p><p>Llev\\\\u00e9 a Alberto a bucear y practicamos algunas habilidades de navegaci\\\\u00f3n para su curso PADI Advanced Open Water Diver.</p><p>La forma en que le estoy ense\\\\u00f1ando a navegar es pr\\\\u00e1ctica. \\\\u00c9l es cart\\\\u00f3grafo, por lo que lo estamos haciendo m\\\\u00e1s interesante y m\\\\u00e1s amplio al mapear las caracter\\\\u00edsticas y atracciones de Ojo De Agua, el \\\\u00e1rea de buceo en la costa en Puerto Morelos, M\\\\u00e9xico.</p><p>Nuestro plan es que ambos nos divirtamos mientras mejoramos nuestras habilidades de navegaci\\\\u00f3n submarina mientras creamos un sendero de buceo que puede ser utilizado para el curso de Navegaci\\\\u00f3n para futuros estudiantes y otras personas que tengan inter\\\\u00e9s en tener un mapa para descubrir la laguna.</p><p>Incluiremos capas de mapas adicionales de fuentes de datos del Parque Nacional y tambi\\\\u00e9n im\\\\u00e1genes y videos interactivos con geoetiquetado para que las personas puedan ver qu\\\\u00e9 diversi\\\\u00f3n pueden tener buceando aqu\\\\u00ed.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "4eb54c2072ec10b38a1e10229760b49edeb597160b8a5b3b24f01de8d2046dbb", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.600995+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.600995+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-09-12"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	Took Alberto on a dive and we practiced some navigation skills for his PADI Advanced Open Water Diver course. The way I'm teaching him navigation is hands on. He's a cartographer so we're making...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/470080524_905321551584817_4076650080467506522_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s590x590_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=127cfc&_nc_ohc=uEUQF4KFvEQQ7kNvwF6Fw45&_nc_oc=AdlVptpH0uMHUSxbT58wvvcTdlge7WbR5mdE2lAXWUVLOgIC39hG2iumx3I8AhZfI-k&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=Q5m2a8eucg1d58eRLL8nsQ&oh=00_AfpU11p_yqCtrA-J_hXgLM_wWzwGe8MjXe1BH28XeOxQEg&oe=696AC8B7