2026-01-12 15:31:01.498083+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.430578+00	e8152265-6580-43c6-a9cd-86255a534017	\N	2022-10-02-my-friend-bill-came-to-visit	My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dive...	published	public	[]	[]	My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dive...	My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dives with Alberto. These guys worked on some skills for their advanced open water and...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-10-02-my-friend-bill-came-to-visit/", "slug": "2022-10-02-my-friend-bill-came-to-visit", "title": "My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dive...", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dive...", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dives with Alberto. These guys worked on some skills for their advanced open water and..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "d71b0e17-73f7-4fda-b852-ad60d4902e1e", "data": {"content": "<p>My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dives with Alberto.  These guys worked on some skills for their advanced open water and nitrox certifications.  We checked out the Juan Escutia and the reef.  They mapped the wreck looking for future places to penetrate making note of hazards and depth while tracking their air and times.  They also learned some about drift diving techniques and the importance of having a DSMB and how to safely shoot the DSMB, paying special heed to how we need to avoid entanglement and an uncontrolled ascent.  We also practiced proper boat diving and surface habits and we experienced a negative entry into current.  These guys made a great buddy team and had a lot of fun in the ocean.  I can't wait to dive with them again!</p><p>---</p><p>Mi amigo Bill vino a visitarnos desde Phoenix y realizamos algunas inmersiones con Alberto. Estos muchachos trabajaron en algunas habilidades para sus certificaciones avanzadas de aguas abiertas y nitrox. Verificamos el Juan Escutia y el arrecife. Mapearon el naufragio en busca de lugares futuros para penetrar tomando nota de los peligros y la profundidad mientras rastreaban su aire y tiempos. Tambi\\\\u00e9n aprendieron algo sobre t\\\\u00e9cnicas de buceo a la deriva y la importancia de tener un DSMB y c\\\\u00f3mo disparar con seguridad el DSMB, prestando especial atenci\\\\u00f3n a c\\\\u00f3mo debemos evitar enredos y un ascenso descontrolado. Tambi\\\\u00e9n practicamos un buen buceo desde barco y h\\\\u00e1bitos de superficie y experimentamos una entrada negativa en la corriente. Estos muchachos formaron un gran equipo de amigos y se divirtieron mucho en el oc\\\\u00e9ano. \\\\u00a1No puedo esperar para bucear con ellos de nuevo!</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "8bc0359bc9c12628940d53271d88689cd7031e4d162cd5b540764bc3757e1cbb", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.503724+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.503724+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-10-02"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	My friend Bill came to visit from Phoenix and we went on a few dives with Alberto. These guys worked on some skills for their advanced open water and nitrox certifications. We checked out the Juan...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/485310233_1036777205135809_1943320452669010030_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p180x540_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=833d8c&_nc_ohc=8_wqjZcbBisQ7kNvwEPhyrZ&_nc_oc=AdnDSWC1qo-DyjNtvv6gHKLfN1OXOS04W-d_w_YXUaARK5FGYYG4wy7pdfYUQ93MK4M&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=onySQa9VEnqm2GdwFhw-vg&oh=00_Afr5nzPzCzjyUAILJ4bR_bjFnM6n0ZTR1N29wetxOquJ7w&oe=696AD472	post	1	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	1ebb6e5c-53b0-41b9-b643-fb7823358e35
