 and possible entry points for penetration.  And to do prior research to find any plans or photos and diagrams to assist with defining primary and secondary objectives during their dive planning.  As a history buff myself, I think it's super cool to find the \\\\</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "00333dde23bc4c97a019c388764dc82ad441547cb60a21624891666e0384e0be", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.543031+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.543031+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-09-21"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	As part of the PADI wreck specialty course I'm preparing to teach I've been researching the wreck here in Puerto Morelos that is going to be my classroom. It has a neat history and after being...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/482089721_1027638222716374_2597480595143148946_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s590x590_tt6&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=127cfc&_nc_ohc=0Y5gn6aY9-4Q7kNvwG9F7jD&_nc_oc=AdkgNKf9QvjzWBt0zhfhpweZe1X8dnvs2c842x8cGjcmlTYAF2-oGpK-F1aJxQTd2Xo&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=Y4CrMbF15XGd40VVGwZz-Q&oh=00_AfpihW77k9Bdnc4eW1NoQFrIMCR3BkCirwYaWoskkHmwEA&oe=696AD524	post	1	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	1ebb6e5c-53b0-41b9-b643-fb7823358e35
