 para un subid\\\\u00f3n de adrenalina ni para deportes de alto riesgo. M\\\\u00e1s bien tener el conocimiento y las herramientas para sobrevivir. Adem\\\\u00e1s, soy un gran nerd y creo que aprender a bucear es s\\\\u00faper interesante y genial.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "668fc733b9243e004600f69e569c7ba9b2d8b2659c524bad54166258ffe9755d", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.445417+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.445417+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-10-12"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	It's Official. Full Cave Diver. Certified to dive safely within my limits with other (more) experienced divers, follow the rules, and avoid injury or death.  I was motivated to continue my...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t15.5256-10/327155641_1318459975670316_3625976375607205104_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_s960x960_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=54741f&_nc_ohc=vdUinJiLVbcQ7kNvwERXPhL&_nc_oc=AdlyXi8vpTLqV7bh1TtFY8fNm8n1ejRFMLTZE1WjHkOKoBBP8EqI2oZHNltZbkdH1R8&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=oE2SAB6YKNTAU7DKvrAsGQ&oh=00_AfrBJ104U8VDXR31PETlfYUi95GMX-3Noqd-31AaXhaU9A&oe=696ACA1F	post	1	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	1ebb6e5c-53b0-41b9-b643-fb7823358e35
