2026-01-12 15:31:01.885271+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.350046+00	b6c8b46f-172d-4ad8-8388-f7f140b4da9c	\N	2022-05-25-wind-fresh-and-the-water-clear	Wind fresh and the water clear. 	published	public	[]	[]	Wind fresh and the water clear. 	Wind fresh and the water clear.  What a great day to practice swimming, skin diving, and dive buddy skills.  Harbor is closed for boats. But swimming...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-05-25-wind-fresh-and-the-water-clear/", "slug": "2022-05-25-wind-fresh-and-the-water-clear", "title": "Wind fresh and the water clear. ", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Wind fresh and the water clear. ", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Wind fresh and the water clear.  What a great day to practice swimming, skin diving, and dive buddy skills.  Harbor is closed for boats. But swimming..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "dc8fef18-bfd8-42d7-a27b-1b3b9b455d01", "data": {"content": "<p>Wind fresh and the water clear.</p><p>What a great day to practice swimming, skin diving, and dive buddy skills.</p><p>Harbor is closed for boats.  But swimming in the waves and current and then hanging out on the resting buoys sure is fun. Being a swimmer is one of the most important skills for diving.  Becoming a strong swimmer takes practice.</p><p>So Kodie and I just finished reviewing these important skills for his open water diver certification.  And he did great in the water! Passed  his swimming tests while having fun.  The swimming test has 2 choices: 1. swim 200 meters without any swimming aids (ie: Laps in the pool) or 2. 300 meters with mask, snorkle and fins.  The float test is float 10 minutes.  It's easy to float in salt water.</p><p>So what better way to enjoy the open water course swimming test than by snorkling an exhilarating ocean drifting down the coast while looking down on some mind-blowing sea creatures on a beautiful day.</p><p>Why swim laps in a pool when you can swim in the ocean, float easily and see cool stuff.!  One on one buddy system i