2026-01-12 15:31:01.657829+00	2026-01-12 15:37:22.394374+00	9eef44c8-c60c-4870-970f-497a667aeedb	\N	2022-09-05-who-wants-to-be-my-dive	Who wants to be my dive buddy?	published	public	[]	[]	Who wants to be my dive buddy?	Who wants to be my dive buddy? If anyone is interested in diving 2 shallow reef sites Wednesday I think mid morning/early afternoon? There is room on a...			index, follow	{"meta": {"path": "/2022-09-05-who-wants-to-be-my-dive/", "slug": "2022-09-05-who-wants-to-be-my-dive", "title": "Who wants to be my dive buddy?", "robots": "index, follow", "seo_title": "Who wants to be my dive buddy?", "og_image_url": "", "seo_description": "Who wants to be my dive buddy? If anyone is interested in diving 2 shallow reef sites Wednesday I think mid morning/early afternoon? There is room on a..."}, "blocks": [{"id": "da9bb038-df2f-453e-9b87-6ef6a41f2d4c", "data": {"content": "<p>Who wants to be my dive buddy?</p><p>If anyone is interested in diving 2 shallow reef sites Wednesday I think mid morning/early afternoon? There is room on a boat for 1 more diver.  It's for a good price of 1000 pesos payable to the operator.</p><p>I'll go with you as your buddy. Especially if you want to get your enriched air (NITROX) cert.  If you've never dived before and have always wanted to try it, and are fit to dive with strong swimming skills, I'll be happy to donate my time and teach you the PADI Discover Scuba Diving course or we can start learning the full open water beforehand (You have to buy the PADI course materials). \\n \\nI'm a PADI instructor in teaching status and am a credentialed guide for the national park. I'm trying to share my love of diving and make new friends who are interested in the amazing resource here.   I'm also an enriched air (NITROX) specialty instructor. If you buy the PADI E-learning, I'll waive the instructor fee during the dives.</p><p>What's the catch?  I am working towards my Master Scuba Diver Trainer and need the experience and student certifications to finish.  So you'll need to be as patient with me as I am with you \\\\ud83d\\\\ude42</p><p>This isn't the only opportunity, so feel free to message me even if you can't go this week but are interested the next time we're trying to fill a boat.</p>"}, "type": "rich_text", "sequence": 0}], "version": 1, "checksum": "aff5bc6a07cdb92b5ba80122ff1dd2888ceb7367e4f5fb8002f652f460e6efb4", "published_at": "2026-01-12T15:31:01.662699+00:00", "access_control": {"level": "public", "required_roles": [], "required_entitlements": []}, "published_by_id": "1"}	2026-01-12 15:31:01.662699+00	0	t	default	{"source": "facebook", "original_date": "2022-09-05"}	1	70c922aa-9fcb-4b5e-8736-e82206cf5c37	Who wants to be my dive buddy? If anyone is interested in diving 2 shallow reef sites Wednesday I think mid morning/early afternoon? There is room on a boat for 1 more diver. It's for a good price...	https://scontent.fcun1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.30808-6/482053802_1030483702431826_1075485034563973875_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p526x296_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=833d8c&_nc_ohc=sZ0Jbim_OZsQ7kNvwHbRUM3&_nc_oc=Adn7JQNK6vakEoW-AKze4jgq1zYSYdvLPm7r9FaHoQPW5fWVTW3chTO7I1HZBinB2Nc&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.fcun1-1.fna&_nc_gid=ZNI9oMyLO4NnuTGipllcGw&oh=00_AfoP4dMNu7nkMDnKchTURRAXgzRrw0dsI6IxqeDLvk0bVQ&oe=696AF45F	post	1	["facebook-import", "buceo-feliz"]	1ebb6e5c-53b0-41b9-b643-fb7823358e35
